## 2. vLLM CUDA Graphs

### 2.1 Architecture

vLLM implements a **multi-mode CUDA graph system** with sophisticated dispatching:

```
CudagraphDispatcher
    ├── NONE: Eager execution (no graphs)
    ├── PIECEWISE: Per-layer graphs (attention excluded)
    ├── FULL: Full model graph
    ├── FULL_DECODE_ONLY: Full graphs for decode, eager for prefill
    └── FULL_AND_PIECEWISE: Full for decode, piecewise for prefill (default)
```

