## 4. TensorRT-LLM CUDA Graphs

### 4.1 Architecture

TensorRT-LLM integrates CUDA graphs at **multiple levels**:

```
TensorRT Runtime
    ├── Automatic graph capture in C++ runtime
    ├── Python CUDAGraphRunner for batch padding
    └── PyTorch CapturedGraph for torch models
```

**Key Feature**: TensorRT can automatically use CUDA graphs when enabled, with minimal configuration.

### 4.2 Core Files

**Location**: `/home/nmiriyal/Documents/UnderstandingVLLM/LatestVLLM/TensorRT-LLM/`

```
tensorrt_llm/runtime/generation.py                       - C++ interop
