- ✨ **Dispatcher architecture**: Intelligent runtime mode selection
- ✨ **Attention backend aware**: Automatic mode downgrade

**SGLang**:
- ✨ **Piecewise CUDA graphs**: Variable prefill length support
- ✨ **Per-shape compilation**: torch.compile + CUDA graph synergy
- ✨ **Hidden state modes**: Dynamic recapture based on requirements

